query:
DELETE FROM
                eth_txs
            WHERE
                id IN (
                    (
                        SELECT
                            eth_commit_tx_id
                        FROM
                            l1_batches
                        WHERE
                            number > $1
                    )
                    UNION
                    (
                        SELECT
                            eth_prove_tx_id
                        FROM
                            l1_batches
                        WHERE
                            number > $1
                    )
                    UNION
                    (
                        SELECT
                            eth_execute_tx_id
                        FROM
                            l1_batches
                        WHERE
                            number > $1
                    )
                )
